    "label": "전체 일정 개요",
    "section": "overview",
    "html": "<div style=\"position:absolute; inset:0.42in; border:1px solid #E4D9C2; pointer-events:none;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; inset:0; padding:0.85in 0.85in 0.62in;\">\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:flex-end; justify-content:space-between; border-bottom:1.5px solid #2C2722; padding-bottom:10px; margin-bottom:14px;\">\n      <h2 style=\"font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif; font-weight:700; font-size:27.5px; margin:0;\">전체 일정 개요</h2>\n      <span style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; font-style:italic; color:#B0492C; font-size:16.5px;\">At a Glance</span>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 18px; font-size:14px; color:#6E6556;\">2026. 6. 30 (화) — 7. 6 (월) · 7일간의 여정</p>\n    <table style=\"width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:14.5px;\">\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th style=\"background:#3A332B; color:#FAF4EA; font-weight:500; padding:9px 10px; text-align:left; width:96px;\">날짜</th>\n          <th style=\"background:#3A332B; color:#FAF4EA; font-weight:500; padding:9px 12px; text-align:left;\">핵심</th>\n          <th style=\"background:#3A332B; color:#FAF4EA; font-weight:500; padding:9px 12px; text-align:left;\">내용</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; white-space:nowrap;\">6/30 <span style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans KR'; font-size:12.5px; color:#6E6556;\">화</span></td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:10px 12px; background:#fff; font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif; color:#8F3F28; white-space:nowrap;\">입국 · 집결</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:10px 12px; background:#fff;\">워싱턴(IAD) 출발 → 과테말라시티(GUA) 도착 · 호텔 체크인</td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; white-space:nowrap;\">7/1 <span style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans KR'; font-size:12.5px; color:#6E6556;\">수</span></td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:10px 12px; background:#fff; font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif; color:#8F3F28; white-space:nowrap;\">개회 · 환영의 밤</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:10px 12px; background:#fff;\">등록 · 미용/의료봉사 · 개회예배 · 환영의 밤</td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; white-space:nowrap;\">7/2 <span style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans KR'; font-size:12.5px; color:#6E6556;\">목</span></td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:10px 12px; background:#fff; font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif; color:#8F3F28; white-space:nowrap;\">집중 사역 · MK</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:10px 12px; background:#fff;\">세미나 · 미용/의료봉사 · MK Child/Youth 프로그램 · 축복의 밤</td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; white-space:nowrap;\">7/3 <span style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans KR'; font-size:12.5px; color:#6E6556;\">금</span></td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:10px 12px; background:#fff; font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif; color:#8F3F28; white-space:nowrap;\">결단 · 파송</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:10px 12px; background:#fff;\">결단의 시간 · 체크아웃 · 사역의 현장으로</td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; white-space:nowrap;\">7/4 <span style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans KR'; font-size:12.5px; color:#6E6556;\">토</span></td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:10px 12px; background:#fff; font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif; color:#8F3F28; white-space:nowrap;\">문화탐방</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:10px 12px; background:#fff;\">안티구아 과테말라 등 현지 문화탐방</td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; white-space:nowrap;\">7/5 <span style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans KR'; font-size:12.5px; color:#6E6556;\">주일</span></td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:10px 12px; background:#fff; font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif; color:#8F3F28; white-space:nowrap;\">현지 교회 방문 · 귀국</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:10px 12px; background:#fff;\">믿음의 비전교회(08:00) · 은혜교회(10:00) 방문 · 한인교회 연합집회(15:00) · 심야 귀국 항공편</td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; white-space:nowrap;\">7/6 <span style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans KR'; font-size:12.5px; color:#6E6556;\">월</span></td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:10px 12px; background:#fff; font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif; color:#8F3F28; white-space:nowrap;\">워싱턴 도착</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:10px 12px; background:#fff;\">워싱턴(IAD) 도착 · 해산</td></tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n    <div style=\"margin-top:20px; background:#F0E7D5; border-left:3px solid #74835F; padding:14px 18px; font-size:14.3px; line-height:1.7; color:#3A332B;\">\n      <strong style=\"font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif; font-weight:700;\">샬롬 핵심 집회</strong>는 7/1(수)–7/3(금) 3일간 호텔 바르셀로에서 진행되며, 이어 7/4 문화탐방과 7/5 주일 한인교회 사역으로 마무리됩니다.\n    </div>"
