    "label": "일정 7/1·7/2",
    "section": "schedule",
    "html": "<div style=\"position:absolute; inset:0.42in; border:1px solid #E4D9C2; pointer-events:none;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; inset:0; padding:0.85in 0.85in 0.62in;\">\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:flex-end; justify-content:space-between; border-bottom:1.5px solid #2C2722; padding-bottom:10px; margin-bottom:22px;\">\n      <h2 style=\"font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif; font-weight:700; font-size:26px; margin:0;\">상세 일정표</h2>\n      <span style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; font-style:italic; color:#B0492C; font-size:15px;\">Daily Schedule</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:baseline; gap:12px; margin-bottom:10px;\">\n      <span style=\"font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif; font-size:19px; color:#B0492C;\">첫째 날</span>\n      <span style=\"font-size:14px; color:#6E6556;\">7/1 (수) · 호텔 바르셀로</span>\n    </div>\n    <table style=\"width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:12.5px; margin-bottom:24px;\">\n      <tbody>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 10px; background:#F0E7D5; width:128px; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#3A332B; white-space:nowrap;\">07:00 — 08:00</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 12px; background:#fff;\">사역 준비</td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#3A332B; white-space:nowrap;\">13:00 —</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 12px; background:#fff;\">등록 및 체크인 · 미용·의료 봉사 ①</td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#3A332B; white-space:nowrap;\">17:00 — 18:00</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 12px; background:#fff;\">휴식</td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#3A332B; white-space:nowrap;\">18:00 — 19:00</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 12px; background:#fff;\">저녁식사</td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#3A332B; white-space:nowrap;\">19:00 — 19:55</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 12px; background:#fff;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:500;\">개회예배</strong> — 박승진 목사 「나의 안에 거하라」 <span style=\"color:#6E6556;\">(요 15:1–9)</span></td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#3A332B; white-space:nowrap;\">20:00 — 21:15</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 12px; background:#fff;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:500;\">환영의 밤</strong> — 릴레이 댄스 · 콩트 · La Gloria de Dios · 합창</td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#3A332B; white-space:nowrap;\">21:00 —</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 12px; background:#fff;\">휴식 및 취침</td></tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:baseline; gap:12px; margin-bottom:10px;\">\n      <span style=\"font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif; font-size:19px; color:#B0492C;\">둘째 날</span>\n      <span style=\"font-size:14px; color:#6E6556;\">7/2 (목) · 세미나 & 축복의 밤</span>\n    </div>\n    <table style=\"width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:12.5px;\">\n      <tbody>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 10px; background:#F0E7D5; width:128px; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#3A332B; white-space:nowrap;\">07:00 — 08:00</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 12px; background:#fff;\">기상 및 아침식사</td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#3A332B; white-space:nowrap;\">08:00 — 09:00</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 12px; background:#fff;\">미용·의료 봉사 ②</td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#3A332B; white-space:nowrap;\">09:40 — 12:00</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 12px; background:#fff;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:500;\">오전 세미나</strong> — 이동원 목사 「만물의 주·믿음의 주 / 생활의 주·선교의 주」</td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#3A332B; white-space:nowrap;\">12:00 — 13:00</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 12px; background:#fff;\">점심식사</td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#3A332B; white-space:nowrap;\">13:00 — 17:00</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 12px; background:#fff;\">미용·의료 봉사 ③④ · 오후 세미나 (김우준 목사)</td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#3A332B; white-space:nowrap;\">18:00 — 19:30</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 12px; background:#fff;\">저녁식사</td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#3A332B; white-space:nowrap;\">19:30 — 21:10</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 12px; background:#fff;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:500;\">축복의 밤</strong> — 이동원 목사 「축제의 공동체」 <span style=\"color:#6E6556;\">(요 2:1–11)</span></td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#3A332B; white-space:nowrap;\">21:00 —</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 12px; background:#fff;\">휴식 및 취침</td></tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>"
