    "section": "",
    "html": "<div style=\"position:absolute; inset:0.42in; border:1px solid #E4D9C2; pointer-events:none;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; inset:0; padding:0.85in 0.85in 0.62in;\">\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:baseline; gap:12px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-top:6px;\">\n      <span style=\"font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif; font-size:19px; color:#B0492C;\">셋째 날</span>\n      <span style=\"font-size:14px; color:#6E6556;\">7/3 (금) · 결단의 시간 & 이동</span>\n    </div>\n    <table style=\"width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:12.5px; margin-bottom:26px;\">\n      <tbody>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 10px; background:#F0E7D5; width:128px; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#3A332B; white-space:nowrap;\">07:00 — 08:00</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 12px; background:#fff;\">기상 및 아침식사</td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#3A332B; white-space:nowrap;\">09:00 — 10:15</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 12px; background:#fff;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:500;\">결단의 시간</strong> — 이수용 목사 · 경배와 찬양 · 기도회</td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#3A332B; white-space:nowrap;\">10:00 — 11:45</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 12px; background:#fff;\">짐 정리 및 체크아웃</td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#3A332B; white-space:nowrap;\">12:00 — 13:00</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 12px; background:#fff;\">점심식사 · 이동</td></tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:baseline; gap:12px; margin-bottom:10px;\">\n      <span style=\"font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif; font-size:19px; color:#B0492C;\">주일 사역</span>\n      <span style=\"font-size:14px; color:#6E6556;\">7/5 (일) · 현지 교회 방문 &amp; 연합집회</span>\n    </div>\n    <table style=\"width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:12.5px; margin-bottom:26px;\">\n      <tbody>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 10px; background:#F0E7D5; width:128px; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#3A332B; white-space:nowrap;\">08:00 — 09:30</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 12px; background:#fff;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:500;\">믿음의 비전교회</strong> <span style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#6E6556;\">(Iglesia Visión de Fe)</span> · 치말테낭고(Chimaltenango)<br/><span style=\"font-size:11px; color:#8F3F28;\">설교 「다시 일어나는 믿음」 <span style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; font-style:italic; color:#9A8E78;\">Faith Rising Again</span> · 요 4:46–54 · 박승진 담임목사</span></td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#3A332B; white-space:nowrap;\">10:00 — 11:30</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 12px; background:#fff;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:500;\">은혜교회</strong> <span style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#6E6556;\">(Iglesia de Gracia)</span> · 치말테낭고(Chimaltenango)<br/><span style=\"font-size:11px; color:#8F3F28;\">설교 「다시 일어나는 믿음」 · 요 4:46–54 · 박승진 담임목사</span></td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 10px; background:#F0E7D5; font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; color:#3A332B; white-space:nowrap;\">15:00 — 16:00</td><td style=\"border:1px solid #DCCFB8; padding:7px 12px; background:#fff;\">과테말라 한인교회 <strong style=\"font-weight:500;\">연합집회</strong> — 이동원 원로목사</td></tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n\n<div style=\"background:#F0E7D5; border-left:3px solid #74835F; padding:14px 18px; font-size:13px; line-height:1.7; color:#3A332B;\">\n      <strong style=\"font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif; font-weight:700;\">안내</strong> &nbsp; 6/30(화)은 과테말라 도착 및 호텔 체크인, 7/6(월)은 새벽 워싱턴 도착 및 해산입니다. 상기 일정은 현지 상황에 따라 조정될 수 있으니, 매 순서 인솔자의 안내를 따라 주시기 바랍니다.\n    </div>"
