    "label": "비상 연락망",
    "section": "contacts",
    "html": "<div style=\"position:absolute; inset:0.42in; border:1px solid #E4D9C2; pointer-events:none;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; inset:0; padding:0.85in 0.85in 0.62in;\">\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:flex-end; justify-content:space-between; border-bottom:1.5px solid #2C2722; padding-bottom:10px; margin-bottom:22px;\">\n      <h2 style=\"font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif; font-weight:700; font-size:26px; margin:0;\">숙소 · 비상 연락망</h2>\n      <span style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; font-style:italic; color:#B0492C; font-size:15px;\">Contacts</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"background:#F0E7D5; border:1px solid #E0D4BC; padding:16px 18px; margin-bottom:22px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px; font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif; font-size:16px;\">바르셀로 과테말라 시티 <span style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; font-style:italic; color:#6E6556; font-size:13px;\">Barceló Guatemala City</span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px; font-size:13px; color:#3A332B; line-height:1.7;\">7A Avenida 15-45, Cdad. de Guatemala 01009 &nbsp;·&nbsp; <span style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif;\">+502-2378-4000</span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0; font-size:12px; color:#6E6556; line-height:1.7; border-top:1px solid #E0D4BC; padding-top:8px;\">숙박 6/30(화) — 7/5(주일) · 조식 호텔 제공 · 타월 세탁 10% 할인 이용 가능</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <h3 style=\"font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif; font-size:17px; margin:0 0 12px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:9px;\"><span style=\"width:9px; height:9px; transform:rotate(45deg); background:#B0492C; display:inline-block;\"></span>긴급 전화 · 대사관</h3>\n\n    <div style=\"border:1px solid #E0D4BC; border-left:3px solid #B0492C; background:#fff; padding:14px 18px; margin-bottom:12px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px; font-weight:700; font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif; font-size:15px;\">주 과테말라 대한민국 대사관</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0; font-size:12.5px; color:#3A332B; line-height:1.8;\">5 Avenida 5-55 Zona 14, Edificio Europlaza, Torre 3, Nivel 7<br/>대표전화 <span style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif;\">+502-2382-4051~4</span> &nbsp;·&nbsp; 영사콜센터(24h) <span style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif;\">+82-2-3210-0404</span></p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"border:1px solid #E0D4BC; border-left:3px solid #74835F; background:#fff; padding:14px 18px; margin-bottom:22px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px; font-weight:700; font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif; font-size:15px;\">주 과테말라 미국 대사관 <span style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif; font-style:italic; color:#6E6556; font-size:12px;\">U.S. Embassy</span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0; font-size:12.5px; color:#3A332B; line-height:1.8;\">Boulevard Austriaco 11-51, Zone 16, Guatemala City<br/>대표전화(24h 긴급 포함) <span style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif;\">+502-2354-0000</span></p>\n    </div>\n\n    <h3 style=\"font-family:'Gowun Batang',serif; font-size:17px; margin:0 0 12px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:9px;\"><span style=\"width:9px; height:9px; transform:rotate(45deg); background:#C18A33; display:inline-block;\"></span>워싱턴 팀 인솔자 연락처</h3>\n    <div style=\"background:#F0E7D5; border:1px solid #E0D4BC; padding:16px 20px;\">\n      <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:baseline; gap:12px; margin-bottom:14px;\"><span style=\"width:88px; font-weight:500; font-size:13.5px;\">인솔자 ①</span><span style=\"flex:1; border-bottom:1px solid #C2B391; height:18px;\"></span></div>\n      <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:baseline; gap:12px;\"><span style=\"width:88px; font-weight:500; font-size:13.5px;\">인솔자 ②</span><span style=\"flex:1; border-bottom:1px solid #C2B391; height:18px;\"></span></div>\n    </div>"
